      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我确认一下当前链路：A(Etcd)→B(LB)→C(Ingress)→D(Ingress)→E(Etcd)→F(Etcd)→G(LB)→H(Worker)→I(Ingress)→J(Worker)。D到E是Ingress连Etcd，这个方向在图里没问题，您担心的是哪个连接？",
